  "reference_number": "INU0319",
  "remarks": "\nIranian Offshore Engineering & Construction Company is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 (“the 2019 Regulations”) on the basis of the following grounds: \n \nIranian Offshore Engineering & Construction Company (IOECC) is or has been making available funds or economic resources that could contribute to a relevant nuclear activity, namely the Islamic Revolutionary Guards Corps’ proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.Iranian Offshore Engineering & Construction Company (IOECC) is or has been making available funds or economic resources that could contribute to a relevant nuclear activity, namely the Islamic Revolutionary Guards Corps’ development of a nuclear weapons delivery system in, or for use in, Iran \n",
